      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty car and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014it's been well-loved and looked after, so it's ready to hit the road with a new owner right away! You might find a tiny bit of character here and there from normal use, but it runs like a dream and has plenty of life left in it. Perfect for someone looking for a reliable ride that still looks great in the driveway. Come take it for a spin!",
