    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "For sale is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This high-revving powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver a linear, visceral power band. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission offers precise shift throws, sending power to the rear wheels through a variable M-differential lock. The chassis has been maintained with an eye toward performance, including proactive rear subframe reinforcement and refreshed suspension bushings to preserve the legendary MacPherson strut and multi-link geometry. While the aesthetic reflects its status as a dedicated driver's car, the drivetrain is robust, providing the tactile steering feedback and throttle response that defines the E46 platform. Recent service includes a valve adjustment and cooling system refresh.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
