    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and daily reliability. The exterior features a deep, lustrous finish that has been regularly waxed, though it shows a few minor stone chips on the front bumper consistent with careful highway driving. Inside, the smoke-free cabin is exceptionally clean; the premium leather seats are soft and supportive, showing only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Mechanically, this car is in solid health, having followed a strict preventative maintenance schedule with full synthetic oil changes every 5,000 miles. The engine is responsive, the transmission shifts seamlessly, and the suspension remains firm and quiet over bumps. All electronics, including the dual-zone climate control and the upgraded infotainment system, are fully functional. This is a turn-key vehicle with a clean title, ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
