    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Offered is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L atmospheric inline-six. This unit delivers linear power delivery to the rear wheels via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis remains composed thanks to refreshed bushings and documented rear subframe reinforcement\u2014a critical preventative measure for this platform. Recent service includes a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and valve clearance adjustment, ensuring the high-revving valvetrain operates with factory precision. While showing minor road wear consistent with its mileage, the mechanical integrity and throttle response remain exceptionally sharp.",
